test_odd_range:
assert [121, 121] == [121, 121, 121, 121, 121]
  Right contains 3 more items, first extra item: 121
  Full diff:
  - [121, 121, 121, 121, 121]
  + [121, 121]
test_all_one_range:
assert [1, 1] == [1, 1, 1, 1, 1]
  Right contains 3 more items, first extra item: 1
  Full diff:
  - [1, 1, 1, 1, 1]
  + [1, 1]
